#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the Contacts pull-down</h2>
The Contacts pull-down has the following options:
<ul>
<li>Download - send vcf file to browser to import into user's contact list
<li>E-mail vcf of contacts to <i>driver</i> - e-mail vcf of contacts to <i>driver</i> to incorporate
into their contact database.
</ul>

